Shout with joy to God all the earth,
Sing glory to His name;
Tell aloud His marvelous worth,
His righteousness proclaim.

Glory and honor
And blessing and power
Be unto the Lord,
Come and let us make
His praise glorious! Glorious!

Shout with joy to God
All the earth,
Sing glory to His name;
Tell aloud His marvelous worth,
His righteousness proclaim.

Glory and honor
And blessing and power
Be unto the Lord,
Come and let us make
His praise glorious! Glorious!

